FBIS4-61876 "drsov091_d_94005" FBIS-SOV-94-091 Daily Report 11 May 1994 Regional Affairs Nonpayments May Force Leningrad Nuclear Station Shutdown Nonpayments May Force Leningrad Nuclear Station Shutdown PM1105102794 Moscow ROSSIYSKIYE VESTI in Russian 11 May 94 p 1 PM1105102794 Moscow ROSSIYSKIYE VESTI Russian BFN [Report from roundup of ITAR-TASS and INTERFAX reports] [Text] The Leningrad nuclear electric power station is on the verge of stoppage as a result of nonpayments by consumers of electricity, who owe the station 250 billion rubles.
